{"id":"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03","title":"第三課：建立應用的房屋位置元件","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"lesson-3-create-the-applications-housinglocation-component\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"844px2atuguxggry4nle52rjc\">第三課：建立應用的房屋位置元件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#lesson-3-create-the-applications-housinglocation-component\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cwzvfvk2vuezzne672ooipcns\">本教程示範瞭如何將 <code>HousingLocation</code> 元件新增到 Angular 應用程式中。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9b0304m4wmxslkazn9h6yr4kn\"><strong>預計時間</strong>: 約10分鐘</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"brbhlzjenxz7qo2sgxm74cy2p\"><strong>初始程式碼：</strong> \n<live-example name=\"first-app-lesson-02\"></live-example></p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bax099u0gliholhwualj5o75w\"><strong>完成的程式碼：</strong> \n<live-example name=\"first-app-lesson-03\"></live-example></p>\n<h2 id=\"what-youll-learn\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cy8qhuh22qozu5okjmjfdf3nx\">你將學到<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#what-youll-learn\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"czdnlc0craxc88h59go4s7k87\">應用程式有一個新元件：<code>HousingLocationComponent</code>，它會顯示一條訊息，以確認該組件成功新增到了應用程式中。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"step-1---create-the-housinglocationcomponent\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"am47ewt7y06hha89z9qcu1upi\">第 1 步 - 建立 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#step-1---create-the-housinglocationcomponent\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c1dvl886e2ctf6tmbj1xjs1uz\">在此步驟中，你將為應用程式建立一個新元件。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8qxzh26n32qnw247t9h8ej3kf\">在 IDE 的<strong>終端</strong>窗格中：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8frcif09w62kpccxwvjafu1rz\">在你的專案目錄中，導向到 <code>first-app</code> 目錄。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cuptbyx5zrgunpo75fin6jzl0\">執行此指令以建立一個新的 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code></p>\n<code-example format=\"shell\" language=\"shell\">\nng generate component housingLocation --inline-template --skip-tests\n</code-example>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8jskza5vthvlm99qlogd8d0tx\">執行此指令以建立並啟動應用開發伺服器。</p>\n<code-example format=\"shell\" language=\"shell\">\n\nng serve\n\n</code-example>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6kseqwn41mvspc1zg321cyaxf\">開啟瀏覽器並導向到 <code>http://localhost:4200</code> 以找到該應用程式。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3s00wy3fxwdxmj22c3073og8v\">確認應用建立時沒有錯誤。</p>\n<div class=\"callout is-helpful\">\n  It should render the same as it did in the previous lesson because even though you added a new component, you haven't included it in any of the app's templates, yet.\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8d2bd58g4jxsvh7kfx1zn5umw\">在完成後續步驟時讓 <code>ng serve</code> 保持執行。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"step-2---add-the-new-component-to-your-apps-layout\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"es22kdzlls6cbepzhe2gkqltg\">第 2 步 - 將新元件新增到應用的佈局中<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#step-2---add-the-new-component-to-your-apps-layout\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ejjlqii2ryk8axsm82eax5y5x\">在此步驟中，你將新元件 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code> 新增到應用的 <code>HomeComponent</code> 中，以便讓它顯示在應用的佈局中。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9r6pgvig5ms9l5ukrbwsza8xg\">在 IDE 的<strong>編輯</strong>窗格中：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"elo5fpzy6g75fztm9mq8i9sg9\">在編輯器中開啟 <code>home.component.ts</code>。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d1aks0n0hh916qqgz6j5eqc9y\">在 <code>home.component.ts</code> 中，透過將此行新增到檔案頂部來匯入 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code>。</p>\n<code-example header=\"Import HousingLocationComponent in src/app/home/home.component.ts\" path=\"first-app-lesson-03/src/app/home/home.component.ts\" region=\"import-housingLocation\">\nimport { HousingLocationComponent } from '../housing-location/housing-location.component';\n\n</code-example>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"32639n4q9t569w8hm5phw0gle\">接下來將 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code> 新增到 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code> 元資料的 <code>imports</code> 陣列中。</p>\n<code-example header=\"Add HousingLocationComponent to imports array in src/app/home/home.component.ts\" path=\"first-app-lesson-03/src/app/home/home.component.ts\" region=\"add-housingLocation-to-array\">\nimports: [\n  <a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">CommonModule</a>,\n  HousingLocationComponent\n],\n\n</code-example>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6w0g1k1x2exb78vur0qjw49dx\">現在該組件已準備好在 <code>HomeComponent</code> 的樣板中使用了。更新 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code> 元資料的 <code>template</code> 屬性，以便包含對 <code>&lt;app-housing-location&gt;</code> 標記的引用。</p>\n<code-example header=\"Add housing location to the component template in src/app/home/home.component.ts\" path=\"first-app-lesson-03/src/app/home/home.component.ts\" region=\"add-housingLocation-to-template\">\ntemplate: `\n  &lt;section&gt;\n    &lt;form&gt;\n      &lt;input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Filter by city\"&gt;\n      &lt;button class=\"primary\" type=\"button\"&gt;Search&lt;/button&gt;\n    &lt;/form&gt;\n  &lt;/section&gt;\n  &lt;section class=\"results\"&gt;\n    &lt;app-housing-location&gt;&lt;/app-housing-location&gt;\n  &lt;/section&gt;\n  `,\n\n</code-example>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"step-3---add-the-styles-for-the-component\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ezkq2efaedzz76f1fkh61aac1\">第 3 步 - 為元件新增樣式<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#step-3---add-the-styles-for-the-component\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7ipt92dypc98y67pnvnxwptwy\">在此步驟中，你會將 <code>HousingLocationComponent</code> 的預寫樣式複製到應用程式中，以便應用程式能正確渲染。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4mcykwh884ompckf9t70r5mqo\">開啟\n<code>src/app/housing-location/housing-location.component.css</code>，並將以下樣式貼上到檔案中：</p>\n<code-example header=\"Add CSS styles to housing location to the component in src/app/housing-location/housing-location.component.css\" path=\"first-app-lesson-03/src/app/housing-location/housing-location.component.css\">\n.listing {\n  background: var(--accent-color);\n  border-radius: 30px;\n  padding-bottom: 30px;\n}\n.listing-heading {\n  color: var(--primary-color);\n  padding: 10px 20px 0 20px;\n}\n.listing-photo {\n  height: 250px;\n  width: 100%;\n  object-fit: cover;\n  border-radius: 30px 30px 0 0;\n}\n.listing-location {\n  padding: 10px 20px 20px 20px;\n}\n.listing-location::before {\n  content: url(\"/assets/location-pin.svg\") / \"\";\n}\n\nsection.listing a {\n  padding-left: 20px;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  color: var(--primary-color);\n}\nsection.listing a::after {\n  content: \"\\203A\";\n  margin-left: 5px;\n}\n\n\n</code-example>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bvylxw9b3bhmrstujsmbt2l22\">儲存你的程式碼，回傳瀏覽器並確認應用程式建立沒有錯誤。你應該看到螢幕上渲染出了訊息 『housing-location works!』。在繼續下一步之前更正所有錯誤。</p>\n<section class=\"lightbox\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ckx8diltvvigud1pco3b7idyn\"><img alt=\"browser frame of homes-app displaying logo, filter text input box and search button and the message 'housing-location works!\" src=\"generated/images/guide/faa/homes-app-lesson-03-step-2.png\" width=\"1640\" height=\"1100\"></section>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"lesson-review\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ckmo8mg671uh3oxv2z72tuj64\">課程回顧<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#lesson-review\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e3eyoufgb3537afso9eyevv8w\">在這節課中，你為應用建立了一個新元件並將其新增到了應用的佈局中。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2vi4aou9du2w1ijyabax7x8qx\">如果你在學習這節課時遇到了任何問題，可以在<live-example></live-example>檢視完整程式碼。</p>\n<h2 id=\"next-steps\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c4pkljueu68ifjoi5994e9l8o\">下一步<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#next-steps\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"alysr3pieonu67oa9r9hb3d20\"><a href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-04\">第一個 Angular 應用程式：第 4 課 - 嚮應用程式新增房屋位置介面</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：Tue Oct 24 2023</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-02\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/core/Component\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#lesson-3-create-the-applications-housinglocation-component\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#lesson-review\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#next-steps\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#step-1---create-the-housinglocationcomponent\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#step-2---add-the-new-component-to-your-apps-layout\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#step-3---add-the-styles-for-the-component\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-03#what-youll-learn\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-04\n-->"}